    <div style="font-size:13px;color:#1a2332;line-height:1.5;margin-top:6px;">Each campaign is measured against its own objective. Lead campaigns show CPL, engagement campaigns show cost per engagement, traffic campaigns show cost per landing page view. Insights use account-relative P25/P75 percentiles with suppression rules - upstream causes override downstream symptoms.</div>
