    <span style="display:inline-block;background:#d1fae5;color:#065f46;font-weight:600;font-size:12px;padding:2px 10px;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:6px;">Finding</span>
    <div style="font-size:13px;color:#1a2332;line-height:1.5;margin-top:6px;">30 leads from $14,863 across 15 ads. Blended CPL: $495. 5 ads spent $1,551 with zero leads.</div>
</div><div class="cards-grid"><div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
        <div class="ad-name">Event_OnlineOH_Image2_v1_2026Apr</div>
        <div class="campaign-name" title="FP_SG_AIS_Conversion_Leads_Prospect_Events, FP_WW_AIS_Conversion_Leads_Retargeting_Events, FP_SG_AIS_Conversion_Leads_Retargeting_Events, FP_WW_AIS_Conversion_Leads_Prospect_Events, FP_ME_AIS_Conversion_Leads_Prospect">FP_SG_AIS_Conversion_Leads_Prospect_Events (+4 more)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-thumbnail"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Event_OnlineOH_Image2_v1_2026Apr" loading="lazy"></div>
